  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Passo 1 — Login",
      "description": "Autentica o cliente e obtém JWT válido por 30 minutos.\n\nConfigure `tax_id_number` + `password` **ou** `email` + `password` nas variáveis da collection.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login com CPF",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    const data = json.data ?? {};",
                  "",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_jwt', data.token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_id', data.id);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_email', data.email ?? '');",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token_expires_at', data.time ?? '');",
                  "",
                  "    pm.test('Login OK — JWT salvo', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(data.token).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "        pm.expect(data.id).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "    });",
                  "",
                  "    console.log('Cliente ID :', data.id);",
                  "    console.log('Email      :', data.email);",
                  "    console.log('Expira em  :', data.time);",
                  "    console.log('Próximo passo: execute \"Obter Conta do Cliente\"');",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 401) {",
                  "    pm.test('401 — verifique X-Token', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect.fail('X-Token ausente ou inválido');",
                  "    });",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 404) {",
                  "    pm.test('404 — cliente não encontrado', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect.fail('CPF ou credenciais incorretos');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tax_id_number\": \"{{tax_id_number}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/customers/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{serverUrl}}/totem"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "customers",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "description": "**Passo 1 do fluxo de acesso à conta.**\n\nAutentica o cliente usando CPF/CNPJ e senha.\n\n### Body\n\n| Campo | Obrigatório | Descrição |\n|-------|-------------|----------|\n| `tax_id_number` | Sim* | CPF ou CNPJ |\n| `password` | Sim | Senha do cliente |\n\n*Use email **ou** CPF — nunca ambos.\n\n### Resposta\n\nSalva automaticamente:\n- `customer_jwt`\n- `customer_id`\n- `customer_email`\n- `token_expires_at`"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login com Email",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    const data = json.data ?? {};",
                  "",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_jwt', data.token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_id', data.id);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_email', data.email ?? '');",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token_expires_at', data.time ?? '');",
                  "",
                  "    pm.test('Login OK — JWT salvo', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(data.token).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "    });",
                  "",
                  "    console.log('Cliente ID :', data.id);",
                  "    console.log('Expira em  :', data.time);",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 401) {",
                  "    console.warn('401: verifique X-Token');",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 404) {",
                  "    console.warn('404: email ou senha incorretos');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/customers/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{serverUrl}}/totem"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "customers",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Alternativa ao login por CPF — autentica usando **email** e senha.\n\nSalva `customer_jwt` automaticamente para o passo 2."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Passo 2 — Consultar Conta",
      "description": "Retorna dados completos do cliente autenticado, incluindo saldo de créditos.\n\n**Requer:** executar o Passo 1 antes (JWT em `customer_jwt`).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Obter Conta do Cliente",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const jwt = pm.collectionVariables.get('customer_jwt');",
                  "",
                  "if (!jwt) {",
                  "    console.warn('⚠ customer_jwt vazio — execute \"Login com CPF\" ou \"Login com Email\" primeiro.');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    const expires = pm.collectionVariables.get('token_expires_at');",
                  "    if (expires) {",
                  "        console.log('JWT expira em:', expires);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    const data = json.data ?? {};",
                  "    const attrs = data.attributes ?? {};",
                  "",
                  "    pm.test('Conta consultada com sucesso', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(data.id).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "        pm.expect(attrs.credits).to.exist;",
                  "    });",
                  "",
                  "    const nome = [attrs['first-name'], attrs['last-name']].filter(Boolean).join(' ');",
                  "",
                  "    console.log('\\n--- Conta do cliente ---');",
                  "    console.log('ID                :', data.id);",
                  "    console.log('Nome              :', nome);",
                  "    console.log('Email             :', attrs.email);",
                  "    console.log('CPF/CNPJ          :', attrs['tax-id-number']);",
                  "    console.log('Saldo de créditos : R$', attrs.credits);",
                  "    console.log('Status            :', attrs.status);",
                  "    console.log('Loja de cadastro  :', attrs['registration-store-code']);",
                  "    console.log('------------------------\\n');",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 401) {",
                  "    pm.test('401 — JWT expirado ou inválido', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect.fail('Execute o login novamente (JWT expira em 30 min)');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{customer_jwt}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/customers/bubble/customer",
              "host": [
                "{{serverUrl}}/totem"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "customers",
                "bubble",
                "customer"
              ]
            },
            "description": "**Passo 2 do fluxo de acesso à conta.**\n\nRetorna dados completos do cliente logado.\n\n### Autenticação (dupla)\n\n```\nX-Token: {{x_token}}\nAuthorization: Bearer {{customer_jwt}}\n```\n\n### Campos principais da resposta\n\n| Campo | Descrição |\n|-------|----------|\n| `attributes.credits` | Saldo de créditos |\n| `attributes.first-name` | Nome |\n| `attributes.last-name` | Sobrenome |\n| `attributes.email` | Email |\n| `attributes.status` | Status da conta |\n| `attributes.registration-store-code` | Loja de cadastro |"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Fluxo completo",
      "description": "Execute esta pasta com **Collection Runner** (Run in order) para simular o fluxo completo:\n\n1. Login com CPF\n2. Obter Conta do Cliente\n\nConfigure `x_token`, `tax_id_number` e `password` antes de rodar.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Login com CPF",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json().data ?? {};",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_jwt', data.token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_id', data.id);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_email', data.email ?? '');",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token_expires_at', data.time ?? '');",
                  "    pm.test('Login OK', () => pm.expect(data.token).to.not.be.empty);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Token",
                "value": "{{x_token}}"
